U9: UNIVERSAL 9-DRIVER IEM

For extreme detail,
precision and clarity

ORDER NOW!

Stealth Series: Custom and Universal In-Ear Monitor Systems

Most people don’t know that your ear is a unique acoustic machine, with a frequency response all its own. And like fingerprints, every ear is different.
That’s why we offer IEMs in both convenient, affordable universal-fit models or custom-tuned systems offering the ultimate in personalization. Choose from three multi-driver configurations, including balanced-armature and hybrid-driver options.

Our Precision-Tuned In-Ear Monitoring Systems use our proprietary SonicFlo technology to engineer second-bend impressions that conform exactly to your inner ear canal, for
superior fidelity, minimal acoustic interference and a perfect fit.

Our universal in-ear monitors offer convenience, customization and value at every price point. All universal IEMs feature Stealth Damping Technology with removable faceplates for
extending bass response, and a variety of cable options to further fine-tune your experience.

All of our custom and universal in-ear monitor systems are built using our Iso-Stealth technology adapted from our aerospace technology innovations, for optimum isolation,
anywhere.
